  <brief_title>Phase II Study of KWA-0711 in Patients With Chronic Constipation (CC)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II, Randomized, Open-label Study of KWA-0711 Administrated Orally for 2 Weeks to Evaluate Its Safety and Efficacy in Patients With Chronic Constipation (CC)</official_title>
